Maintainer: Harlan Williams <harlanrhwilliams@gmail.com>
Date: 2024-08-22
Description: This package provides a set of functions to help users perform
    requests to the Arctos API to download data. It provides a set of builder
    classes for performing complex requests, as well as a set of simple
    functions for automating many common requests and workflows.
